{"tid":1118932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"返大陸拜山，見到D公廁，笑咗出黎","createTime":"2019-04-21T15:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T08:13:27.000Z","uid":149494,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"79bbdfcc23f91f55924f6c0547533054369f7e85","tid":1118932,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"返大陸拜山，個場勁撚多人，仲要幾多靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁突然人有三急，想搵個地方屙屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都估到大陸D公廁唔方乾淨架啦，但應該無以前D人講得咁差掛, 大陸近年發展得咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁9秒9衝入男廁啦，屌奶星，一入到去見到條尿嘈，勁撚黃，仲要有屎漬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n妖, 即刻擰轉面搵屙屎既地方, 屌!!!!<br />\n竟然係踎厠...仲要無門..得塊板仔遮住D人個屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好清楚見到每一個踎住屙緊屎既麻甩佬個樣同個身,,,<br />\n最癲既係,,有條友唔知點解踎得勁後..塊板遮唔到佢屎忽...見到佢條屎痴住響屎忽到屙緊出黎...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚇到我即刻衝撚咗出去..<br />\n跟住我問我阿妹,女厠係咪都係咁..佢話係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc1b6d7b00cb81012401995ecde05884fc63de7","tid":1118932,"uid":20659,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T15:32:53.000Z","msg":"支那狗係用呢種廁所架啦"},{"pid":"aa62cce1beb3ac3da9c016a0437457b3f283b4a1","tid":1118932,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T15:34:08.000Z","msg":"They don&rsquo;t use toilet"},{"pid":"61bbee2c5f4d71ce796910b8751a1a02194bb346","tid":1118932,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T15:39:25.00